{"tid":980134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉載】美國《福布斯》評選「全世界25個最聰明國家」　日本勇奪第一","createTime":"2019-01-13T09:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T04:57:31.000Z","uid":78806,"like":82,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"a8de6c9f2199663cdab154b95c59baf7a35d3eab","tid":980134,"uid":78806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:36:19.000Z","msg":"2019-01-13 <br />\n<br />\n全球最聰明的國家位於亞州？根據福布斯最新出爐的排行榜，日本勇奪第一。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國《福布斯》(Forbes) 公布「全世界25個最聰明國家」名單，在最聰明國家的排名上，前五位的分别是日本、瑞士、中國、美國和荷蘭。 <br />\n<br />\n研究人員編制了一份有25個「最聰明選項」的清單。他們的結論基於三個因素：諾貝爾獎得獎人數、人民的平均智商，以及在學校的學習成績。 <br />\n<br />\n在最聰明國家的排名上，日本排在第一位；在諾貝爾獎獲得者數量一項上，美國則位居榜首；在學校教育水平這一項上，新加坡則排在第一位。 <br />\n<br />\n正如榜單的編制者們所解釋的那樣，這些數據可以讓人了解一個國家的過去、現在和未來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「全世界25個最聰明國家」排行榜（圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dB9O3GH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdB9O3GH.jpg&h=1261ff1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRanked: The 25 Smartest Countries In The World<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/duncanmadden/2019/01/11/ranked-the-25-smartest-countries-in-the-world\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fduncanmadden%2F2019%2F01%2F11%2Franked-the-25-smartest-countries-in-the-world&d=bgVAGvIKTpLDxAMLclI%2B7tibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=dc107a62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/duncanmadden/2019/01/11/ranked-the-25-smartest-countries-in-the-world</a>"},{"pid":"4fa378fd8036f9e2cf9876ee62ad4e471676c50a","tid":980134,"uid":1482,"like":21,"dislike":9,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"台灣no.1"},{"pid":"178416833686cbfb2b17c65a52027a0f346159d2","tid":980134,"uid":14719,"like":133,"dislike":3,"score":130,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"香港同台灣差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9492e56b18d90967af20ad3c80ed5835f508c841","tid